    <item>
      <title>如果媒体“专业”，香港将搁置假新闻法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/hong-kong-will-shelve-fake-news-law-if-media-is-professional</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港领导人表示，只要媒体自律，金融中心就不会通过假新闻法，这表明政府已暂停三年前提出的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/hong-kong-will-shelve-fake-news-law-if-media-is-professional</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 04:51:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布林肯访华前夕，中国谴责美国产能过剩的说法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/china-condemns-us-s-overcapacity-claim-just-before-blinken-visit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国对美国对工业产能过剩的抱怨发起了迄今为止最严厉的攻击，这表明国务卿安东尼·布林肯在本周访问期间可能会进行一些艰难的对话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/china-condemns-us-s-overcapacity-claim-just-before-blinken-visit</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 04:50:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国向美国施加压力，要求其加强基辅防空援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/germany-raises-pressure-on-us-to-step-up-kyiv-air-defense-aid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，德国总理奥拉夫·肖尔茨政府正在敦促美国向乌克兰提供至少一套爱国者反导系统，以帮助缩小俄罗斯在升级一系列攻击之际的防空差距。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/germany-raises-pressure-on-us-to-step-up-kyiv-air-defense-aid</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 04:48:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国称俄罗斯拥抱朝鲜可能会增强金正恩的勇气</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/russia-s-north-korea-embrace-could-embolden-kim-jong-un-us-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府一名高级官员表示，俄罗斯“完全拥抱”朝鲜可能会增加金正恩在威胁韩国和向海外出口武器方面的风险偏好，并帮助平壤无视华盛顿重返核谈判的呼吁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/russia-s-north-korea-embrace-could-embolden-kim-jong-un-us-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 01:30:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>米莱在阿根廷电视讲话中宣扬季度预算盈余</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/milei-trumpets-quarterly-budget-surplus-in-argentina-tv-address</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统哈维尔·米莱在电视讲话中宣布阿根廷自 2008 年以来首次实现季度财政盈余，并承诺在整个任期内消除赤字的承诺不会动摇。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/milei-trumpets-quarterly-budget-surplus-in-argentina-tv-address</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 01:20:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克在悉尼持刀袭击帖子的澳大利亚法庭听证会上失败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/musk-loses-australia-court-hearing-on-sydney-knife-attack-posts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 的社交网络 X 遭到澳大利亚法院的临时禁令，要求其删除刺伤袭击的视频，这引发了该社交网络所有者的愤怒回应，指责政府进行审查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/musk-loses-australia-court-hearing-on-sydney-knife-attack-posts</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 00:58:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哥伦比亚大学和耶鲁大学对亲巴勒斯坦抗议者采取强硬态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/columbia-protests-robert-kraft-criticizes-school-as-yale-cracks-down</link>
